            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)截至台北時間27日21:30股價上漲8.84美元，報157.69美元，漲幅5.94%，成交量6,351,412（股），盤中最高價157.71美元、最低價155.54美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.21%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.03%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.21%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.14%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+9.29%</li> <li>近 1 月：+14.03%</li> <li>近 3 月：-3.67%</li> <li>近 6 月：-11.89%</li> <li>今年以來：-12.98%</li></ul></section></main>",
